  add
  
  T 15 get
]
/T C 1 get def
% T = T^-1
% => R^-1 T^-1 
[
  R 0 get T 0 get mul
  R 3 get T 4 get mul add
  R 6 get T 8 get mul add
  
  R 0 get T 1 get mul
  R 3 get T 5 get mul add
